/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 50 800 Tm (# Docker + Kubernetes + Dhan API \(Future\) Guide) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 786 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 772 Tm (This guide deploys the Streamlit app with Docker and Kubernetes, routes traffic from `chandudevopai.shop`, and keeps a future-ready Dhan API tab in the app.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 758 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 744 Tm (## 1\) Local Docker run) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 730 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 716 Tm (```bash) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 702 Tm (cd /opt/intratrade) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 688 Tm (vim deploy/docker/Dockerfile) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 674 Tm (vim deploy/docker/docker-compose.yml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 660 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 646 Tm (# Build image) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 632 Tm (docker build -f deploy/docker/Dockerfile -t intratrade:latest .) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 618 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 604 Tm (# Run container) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 590 Tm (docker compose -f deploy/docker/docker-compose.yml up -d) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 576 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 562 Tm (# Verify) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 548 Tm (docker ps) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 534 Tm (docker logs intratrade_app --tail 100) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 520 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 506 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 492 Tm (Open `http://<server-ip>:8501`.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 478 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 464 Tm (## 2\) Kubernetes deployment \(single node or cluster\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 450 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 436 Tm (```bash) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 422 Tm (cd /opt/intratrade) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 408 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 394 Tm (# Create namespace + config) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 380 Tm (kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/namespace.yaml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 366 Tm (kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/configmap.yaml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 352 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 338 Tm (# Create secrets from template) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 324 Tm (cp deploy/k8s/secret.example.yaml deploy/k8s/secret.yaml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 310 Tm (vim deploy/k8s/secret.yaml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 296 Tm (kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/secret.yaml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 282 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 268 Tm (# Apply workload) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 254 Tm (kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/deployment.yaml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 240 Tm (kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/service.yaml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 226 Tm (kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/ingress.yaml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 212 Tm (kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/hpa.yaml) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 198 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 184 Tm (# Verify) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 170 Tm (kubectl get all -n intratrade) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 156 Tm (kubectl get ingress -n intratrade) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 142 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 128 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 114 Tm (## 3\) Push image to registry \(recommended\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 100 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 86 Tm (```bash) Tj
ET
