1 0 0 1 50 660 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 646 Tm (Set DNS A record:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 632 Tm (- Host: `chandudevopai.shop`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 618 Tm (- Value: your load balancer/public IP) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 604 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 590 Tm (If using NGINX ingress controller, ensure ports 80/443 are open.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 576 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 562 Tm (For TLS \(HTTPS\):) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 548 Tm (- Install cert-manager in cluster.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 534 Tm (- Add TLS secret and issuer in ingress manifest.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 520 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 506 Tm (## 5\) App feature included for future Dhan API) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 492 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 478 Tm (The app now includes strategy tab:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 464 Tm (- `Dhan API \(Future\)`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 450 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 436 Tm (Inside that tab:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 422 Tm (- Auth panel for `client_id` and access token) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 408 Tm (- Market feed contract example) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 394 Tm (- Order router payload example) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 380 Tm (- Webhook event schema example) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 366 Tm (- Downloadable `dhan_order_template.csv`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 352 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 338 Tm (Current status:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 324 Tm (- Dhan tab is scaffold-only \(safe for future extension\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 310 Tm (- Existing bots continue to run normally) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 296 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 282 Tm (## 6\) Useful operations) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 268 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 254 Tm (```bash) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 240 Tm (# Restart app deployment) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 226 Tm (kubectl rollout restart deployment intratrade-app -n intratrade) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 212 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 198 Tm (# Follow logs) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 184 Tm (kubectl logs -f deployment/intratrade-app -n intratrade) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 170 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 156 Tm (# Scale manually) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 142 Tm (kubectl scale deployment intratrade-app --replicas=2 -n intratrade) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 128 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 114 Tm (# Remove everything) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 100 Tm (kubectl delete ns intratrade) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 86 Tm (```) Tj
